sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Endpoint
    participant Mediator
    participant Handler
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    
    Client->>Endpoint: POST /api/properties
    Endpoint->>Mediator: Send(CreatePropertyCommand)
    Mediator->>Handler: Handle(Command)
    Handler->>DB: SaveChanges()
    DB-->>Handler: Success
    Handler-->>Mediator: Response (DTO)
    Mediator-->>Endpoint: Response (DTO)
    Endpoint-->>Client: 200 OK + ApiResponse
